x^2\,dx + (xy + x^2)\,dy = 0
z = y/x
 \frac{dy}{dx} = -\frac{x^{2}}{xy+x^{2}} = -\frac{1}{\frac{y}{x} + 1}. 
 x\frac{dz}{dx} + z = - \frac{1}{z+1}. 
u = \frac{z+\frac{1}{2}}{\sqrt{\frac{3}{4}}}
 \int \frac{(z+1)}{z(z+1)+1}dz = -\int \frac{1}{x} = -\mathrm{ln}(x) + C 
 \frac{(z+1)}{z(z+1)+1} = \frac{4}{3}\frac{(z+1)}{\left(\frac{z+\frac{1}{2}}{\sqrt{3/4}}\right)^{2}+1}.  
 \frac{4}{3}\frac{\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}u+\frac{1}{2}}{u^{2}+1}= \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\frac{u+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}}{u^{2}+1} 
 \int \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\frac{u+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}}{u^{2}+1}\sqrt{\frac{3}{4}}du = -\mathrm{ln}(x) + C 
 \int \frac{u}{u^{2}+1} du + \frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\int \frac{1}{u^{2}+1}du   
 \left[\frac{1}{2}\mathrm{ln}\left(u^{2}+1\right)+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\mathrm{arctan}(u) \right] = -\mathrm{ln}(x) + C 
 u = \frac{1}{x}\frac{2y+x}{\sqrt{3}} 
 \left[\frac{1}{2}\mathrm{ln}\left(\left(\frac{1}{x}\frac{2y+x}{\sqrt{3}}\right)^{2}+1\right)+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\mathrm{arctan}\left(\frac{1}{x}\frac{2y+x}{\sqrt{3}}\right) \right] = -\mathrm{ln}(x) + C 
 \left(\frac{1}{x}\frac{2y+x}{\sqrt{3}}\right)^{2}+1 = \frac{4y^{2} + 4xy + x^{2} + 3x^{2}}{3x^{2}} = \frac{4}{3}\frac{y^{2} + xy + y^{2}}{x^{2}} 
 \mathrm{ln}\left(\frac{4}{3}\right) + \mathrm{ln}\left(\frac{y^{2} + xy + y^{2}}{x^{2}}\right) 
 \frac{1}{2}\mathrm{ln}\left(\frac{y^{2} + xy + y^{2}}{x^{2}}\right)+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\mathrm{arctan}\left(\frac{1}{x}\frac{2y+x}{\sqrt{3}}\right)  = -\mathrm{ln}(x) + C 
